Text.string: Another day living the refugee lifestyle!
It's nice when it's dark. Makes the barrel fires cozier.
Things aren't so bad!||—I dunno why I said that, it's all pretty bad.
The other day, I popped a Maliwan dude and his head flew off, heh! It was awesome.
Maliwan can kiss my pimpled ass.
I'm always ready for a fight!
Go make a mess out there, Vault Hunter!
I'd pay good money to see you in action.
Just wanna go back to a normal life, is that so much to ask?
You see a Maliwan soldier, you plug 'em for me, okay?
Living this close to death really makes you appreciate every moment.
I'd love to get out there some time and kick some ass with you.
We're gonna take our city back from those bastards.
I can't wait to get back out there.
When we set back down on Promethea, I'm ready for the front lines.
I should get back to Promethea one of these days and kill some more Maliwan assholes.
You headin' back to Promethea at any point? Take me with you when you do.
I actually kinda miss that war-torn hellhole of a city. Weird, right?
I hope the old discotheque down in Meridian didn't get destroyed in the fighting. That place was lit!
Keep your head down out there!
Don't do anything I wouldn't do—which is basically nothing! So, go nuts!
Don't let the haters hate. You do you!
What was I doing? It was... nope, I lost it.
I wonder who's hosting the barrel fire tonight.
I'd waste so many Maliwan if I just had a better gun.
War is supposed to be good for the economy, right?
Maliwan's gonna take one look at me and run the other way.
Had to kill a few ratch the other day. Man, those things are disgusting.
Things could be worse. I could still be a writer. Ugh. I'll take refugee any day.
Feels like I'm missing something... oh, right, all my worldly possessions.
Gotta be some way to turn this mess into an advantage. I know! An app. Just gotta make it and figure out what it does.
I could really go for a Dynasty Burger right now.
Atlas'll do right by us. They've got to.
I wish I had Siren powers.
I'm so ready for the front lines.
[burp] Ugh... when did I eat fish?
Hey, tell me a joke! I need to laugh.
